        "TileImage": "$($repository 7433853d-2251-4267-9593-1a0c15902003).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon,47. Congratulations on your success in Bangkok. We managed to discover two more agents working for the cult in Santa Fortuna. Your targets are Catalina Delgado, wife of  Rico Delgado and Javier Pedroza, mansion guard closely connected to Delgado family. We learned that both of them will exchange a viral transaction for the serum shipments. Ether also informed that the serum is weak when in contact with water, that&apos;s why they demand all the targets on being drowned. Good luck, 47.",
